  "prompt": "How do I check my last 3 charges in Vodafone?",
  "response": "To check your last 3 charges on Vodafone, you can use one of the following methods:\n\n### 1. **My Vodafone App**\n   - Download and log in to the **My Vodafone App** (available on iOS and Android).\n   - Navigate to the **Billing** or **Usage** section.\n   - Look for recent charges or transactions to view your last 3 charges.\n\n### 2. **Online Account**\n   - Log in to your **Vodafone account** via the official website.\n   - Go to the **Billing** or **Account Summary** section.\n   - Check your recent transactions or charges.\n\n### 3. **Customer Service**\n   - Call Vodafone customer service at **191** (from your Vodafone number) or **+44 (0) 333 3040 191** (from any other phone).\n   - Speak to a representative and ask for details of your last 3 charges.\n\n### 4. **Text Message**\n   - You may send a text with a specific keyword (e.g., \"BILL\") to a Vodafone shortcode (check Vodafone's website for the correct keyword and number).\n   - You\u2019ll receive a message with your recent charges.\n\n### 5. **USSD Code**\n   - Dial **#111#** from your Vodafone number and follow the on-screen prompts to view your billing details or recent charges.\n\nIf you\u2019re unsure about any of these methods, contact Vodafone customer support for assistance.",
